title: The Weakest Link - Eastenders Special
description:
The Weakest Link - Eastenders Special (26th June 2008)


EastEnders Special.
Anne Robinson presents a special EastEnders edition of the quick-fire general knowledge quiz. Nine stars, including Bobby Davro, Gemma Bissix, Charlie Clements, Joe Swash and Linda Henry, test their wits against TV&#039;s Queen of Mean. Will they end up wishing they&#039;d never left the relative happiness of Albert Square?
